  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Continue and deepen dialogue among key political actors with a view to building trust and forging consensus on contentious constitutional issues;Facilitate processes which aim at including in the constitution aspects which support managing diversity, accountability, and public participation; Support the transition from constitution making to the next elections by continuing through the period of transition to facilitate dialogues and support preparations for implementing the newly agreed constitution;Support the implementation of constitutional design which accommodates diversity, especially affirmative action legislation and policies and language policies; and Assist and encourage the new legislature in implementing the institutional framework established by the new or revised constitution."
    },
